    <body>
        <div id="intro-div">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div id="description" class="col-12 col-lg-8">
                        
                        <h1 class="roboto-light">CURS GRATUIT</h1>
                        <h2 class="roboto-bold">cu Igret Paul</h2>
                        <p class="roboto-regular">Descopera <span>metoda simpla si eficienta</span> care te ajuta sa arzi calorii rapid si sa-ti tonifiezi corpul in doar <span>10 minute de sarit coarda pe zi</span>.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div id="logo-div" class="col-12 col-lg-4">
                        <img src="images/logo_final.png" height="450" id="logo" alt="Logo">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger btn-lg">DESCARCA CURSUL</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pb-5" id="section2">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="m-2">Ce vei invata in acest curs?</h1>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                        <div class="card mt-3">
                            <img src="/images/section2_image1.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Card Image">
                            <div class="card-img-overlay card-box">
                                <h3 class="card-title">Cum sa alegi, ajustezi, sari coarda</h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                        <div class="card mt-3">
                            <img src="/images/section2_image2.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Card Image">
                            <div class="card-img-overlay card-box">
                                <h3 class="card-title">Care sunt beneficiile saritului corzii</h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                        <div class="card mt-3">
                            <img src="/images/section2_image3.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Card Image">
                            <div class="card-img-overlay card-box">
                                <h3 class="card-title">Cum sa te antrenezi rapid corect si eficient</h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-5" id="section3">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="m-3 row">
                    <div class="col=12 col-lg-4">
                        <img src="/images/section3.jpeg" alt="Paul">
                    </div>
                    <div id="about-me-div" class="col-12 col-lg-8">
                        <h1>Despre mine</h1>
                        <p><span>Peste 2 ani de experienta</span> in domeniul saritului cu coarda.</p>
                        <p>Antrenor de sarit coarda <span>certificat</span> international.</p>
                        <p>Fondatorul programului <span>"Jump and Joy"</span>, specializat in slabire si tonifierea muschilor.</p>
                        <p>Am antrenat <span>peste 50 de persoane</span> care au descoperit beneficiile saritului cu coarda si si-au transformat stilul de viata.</p>
                        <p>Particip activ la <span>competitii internationale</span> de sarit coarda.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h3>Introdu mai jos adresa ta de e-mail pentru a-ti putea trimite cursul.</h3>
                    <form action="/submit" method="POST">
                        <div id="" class="input-group mb-3"> 
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Email">
                            <button class="btn btn-outline-success" type="submit">Submit</button> 
                        </div>
                    </form>
            </div>
        </div>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
